nodes.text: This unidentified Sullustan rebel was recruited to join the Rebel Alliance's new fighting unit, Renegade Squadron. He fought with Renegade Squadron when they were ambushed on Ord Mantell. He survived through the Battle of Endor.

Although it is unconfirmed, It appears quite likely this Sullustan is in fact Ten Numb. He wears the same red B-wing pilot uniform that Ted Numb wears in his screen appearance in Return of the Jedi. Furthermore, in every cutscene in which the unnamed Sullustan rebel in Renegade Squadron appears, he seems to be a hand drawn mirror image of the picture of Ten Numb shown on his original Topps Return of the Jedi trading card.
